metadata.name: Merakhi Genesis #1
metadata.description: 1000 Agata Monkeyz living in the Merakhi Realm.  A whole ecosystem built for our community. A collection of Agata Monkeyz that are living peacefully in the Merakhi realm or are they? With amazing features that give you access to our simulation-Multiplayer Game, a Unique token system, and much more.  A Beautiful tale in which the fates of Agata and Wraith intertwine... begins now! Join the Realm and Build with US!
